Remarks. Previous records on the coast of São Paulo state include Ubatuba ( Mantelatto & Fransozo 2000 ; Bertini & Fransozo 2004; Bertini et al. 2004, 2010;
Mantelatto et al. 2004b
;
Alves et al. 2012b
, 2013b ), Ilha das Couves and Ilha Rapada (
