Braga et al. 2005
). Its presence in Argentina needs to be validated (
Spivak et al. 2019
). Guinot (2012) transferred the genus
Stenorhynchus
from Inachidae to Inachoididae on the basis of adult and larval morphology and behavior. Sequences accession number (GenBank): CCDB 3953—16S ( MF490218 ), COI ( MF490122 ) (
Mantelatto et al. 2018a
